31 Hetuduka, Maggārammaṇattika
Hetuduka, Maggārammaṇattika
78.
189Nahetuṃ namaggārammaṇaṃ dhammaṃ paccayā hetu maggārammaṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā tīṇi…pe…  avigate tīṇi.
